<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>بِسْمِ اللَّهِ الرَّحْمنِ الرَّحِيمِ ... نَسْتَعِينُ ١- ٤/ ٤ ١٧٠.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>صِراطَ الَّذِينَ أَنْعَمْتَ عَلَيْهِمْ ٧- ٣ ١٤٥<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c4">[سورة البقرة]</span><a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>الم ذلِكَ الْكِتابُ لا رَيْبَ فِيهِ ... بِالْغَيْبِ ١- ٣ ٤/ ٣٨٩.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>كُلَّما أَضاءَ لَهُمْ مَشَوْا فِيهِ ٢٠ ٤/ ٢٦٩.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>إِنْ كُنْتُمْ فِي رَيْبٍ ... ٢٣ ٤/ ١٤٠، ١٨١، ٢٢٠، ٢٣٣،<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>٢٣٥، ٢٣٦- ٤/ ٣٨١- ٩/ ٣٩، ٤٠.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>فَإِنْ لَمْ تَفْعَلُوا وَلَنْ تَفْعَلُوا ٢٤ ٤/ ٢٢٠.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>يا آدَمُ ٣٣ ٤/ ١٨٥.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>اسْتَعِينُوا بِالصَّبْرِ وَالصَّلاةِ ٤٥ ١١/ ١٠.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>لا يُقْبَلُ مِنْها شَفاعَةٌ ٤٨ ٤/ ٢٦٠.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>لَنْ نُؤْمِنَ لَكَ حَتَّى نَرَى اللَّهَ جَهْرَةً ٥٥ ٣/ ١٣٢.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>ادْخُلُوا الْبابَ سُجَّداً وَقُولُوا حِطَّةٌ ٥٨ ١/ ٢٨٢- ١٣/ ٣٢٢- ٣٢٤.<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>تَشابَهَ عَلَيْنا ٧٠ ٤/ ٢٥٢.<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>يُحَرِّفُونَهُ مِنْ بَعْدِ ما عَقَلُوهُ ٧٥ ٣/ ١٧٩.<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>وَإِذا لَقُوا الَّذِينَ آمَنُوا قالُوا.. ١٤ ٧٦ ٤/ ٢١٨.<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span>أَوَلا يَعْلَمُونَ أَنَّ اللَّهَ يَعْلَمُ ما يُسِرُّونَ ٧٧ ٤/ ٢١٨<a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>